Package: suggestK
Type: Package
Title: Crawl and Visualize Related Search Terms from the Major Search Engines in Korea
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Lee
Maintainer: Victor Lee <kwangchun.lee.7@gmail.com>
Description: Crawl related search terms from the major search engines; Google, Naver, and Daum. 
    Because the major search engines in Korea have different interfaces, 
    each has its own crawling functions.
    The crawling function returns dataframe suitable for network visualization.
    Based on the tidy dataframe, it supports the network visualization 
    and interactive traverse of search terms.
License: GPL-3
Depends: tidyverse, igraph, glue, urltools, rvest, qdapTools, httr, networkD3, devtools
Imports: tidyverse, igraph, glue, urltools, rvest, qdapTools, httr, networkD3, devtools
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
